IOWA RIGHT TO LIFE COMMITTEE, INC., petitioner,
v.
Megan TOOKER, in Her Official Capacity as Iowa Ethics and Campaign Disclosure Board Executive Director, et al. No. 13-407. Supreme Court of the United States April 7, 2014.

Case below, 717 F.3d 576.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
